This loop launches the Generic Batch Trade site and tries 3 times in  using the vRetryGBTLaunch counter variable if the launch was unsuccessful.
If the verify button is present, we can confirm that the site was launched successfully and exit the loop

Increment the retry counter variable so the loop stops at 4

This if statements checks to see if the RetryGBTLaunch Counter variable reached 4, if the counter got to 4 we can assume that GBT did not launch successfully, so the next step logs to the error log, stops the process and sends an email to RPA Support, however if the counter variable did not reach 4, we can assume the launch was succesful and we can log to the error log
If vRetryGBTLaunch is = to 4 , log to error log after unsuccesful launch of GBT
If vRetryGBTLaunch is = to 4 ,email unsuccesful launch of GBT
If vRetryGBTLaunch is not = to 4 ,log succesful launch of GBT
